                \n                \n                \n                </li>\n            </ul>\n        </li>   \n        <li class=\"title\">\n\n            <a class=\"a\" href=\"../../tzgg.htm\" title=\"通知公告\"><h3>通知公告</h3></a><i></i>\n        </li>   \n    </ul>\n</nav>\n<section class=\"nav_mask\"></section>\n\n<!--============================头部 结束=============================-->\n\n\n<!--============================主体 开始=============================-->\n\n<section id=\"banner\" class=\"banner\">\n     <ul class=\"slow_miso miso-initialized miso-slider\">\n        <div aria-live=\"polite\" class=\"miso-list draggable\"><div class=\"miso-track\" role=\"listbox\" style=\"opacity: 1; width: 1280px; transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px);\"><li class=\"miso-slide miso-current miso-active\" data-miso-index=\"0\" aria-hidden=\"false\" tabindex=\"-1\" role=\"option\" aria-describedby=\"miso-slide00\" style=\"width: 1280px;\">\n <a tabindex=\"0\">\n            <img src=\"../../images/banner/ban7ner.jpg\" alt=\"\"> </a>\n        </li></div></div>\n    </ul> \n\n</section>\n<script>\n$(\".banner ul\").miso({\n    dots:true\n});\n</script>\n\n<section class=\"miso_content\">\n\n<section class=\"n_container n_lvli_detail\">\n    <div class=\"w1200\">\n        <div class=\"content\">\n            <div class=\"bg\"></div>\n            <div class=\"content_li\">\n                <div class=\"title001\">\n                    <h3>\n\n\n\n肿瘤生物学</h3>\n                </div>\n \n             \n                <div class=\"fl00 fl01 clearfix\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/interface/NewsvoteDWR.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/engine.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/news/newscontent.js\"></script><link href=\"/system/resource/style/component/news/content/format4.css\" type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/ajax.js\"></script><form name=\"_newscontent_fromname\">\n<div class=\"left fl\">\n                        <div class=\"img slow fl\">\n                                                    <img src=\"/__local/B/AB/F1/D7DB047F6E675F8D5BDB07FA9D6_E72ACD6C_297D4.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-bottom: #39b54a 3px solid;\">\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"con fr\">\n                            <h3>朱佳俊</h3>\n                            <dl><dd>清华大学基础医学院，助理教授</dd>\n                            \n                            </dl>                            \n                            <p>\n                                <b>Contact Us：</b><br>\n                              \n                                E-mail:  zhujiajun@tsinghua.edu.cn<br>\n                                Address：中国北京市海淀区清华大学医学科学楼\n                            </p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"right fr\">\n \n       \n\n       \n\n\n\n\n<div id=\"vsb_content_4\"><div class=\"v_news_content\">\n<div>\n <h4 style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">教育背景</h4>\n <p>2006-2010 清华大学生命学院 学士</p>\n <p>2007-2010 清华大学经济管理学院 第二学士</p>\n <p>2010-2016 美国宾夕法尼亚大学 博士</p>\n <p>2010-2016 美国宾夕法尼亚大学沃顿商学院 硕士</p>\n <h4 style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">工作经历</h4>\n <p>2016-2021 美国纪念斯隆-凯特琳癌症中心 博士后研究员</p>\n <p>2021-2024 清华大学医学院 助理教授</p>\n <p>2024-至今 清华大学基础医学院 助理教授</p>\n <h4 style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">研究领域</h4>\n <p>朱佳俊博士的重点研究领域是从细胞新陈代谢角度探究人类疾病发生的分子机理。人体内各式各样的细胞对营养物质的获取和利用为几乎一切生理病理过程提供物质和能量基础。朱佳俊博士及其课题组以分子生物学和细胞生物学为主要技术手段，辅以代谢组学和动物模型，从哺乳动物细胞代谢角度研究基本的生物学问题和生命现象，并以能增进对肿瘤等疾病的认知和临床治疗为目标。</p>\n <h4 style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">科学贡献</h4>\n <p>发现或阐明细胞响应氨基酸等营养物质含量变化的代谢调控机制，细胞内区室化的氧化还原调控范式，以及这些营养物质调控机理在肿瘤进程中的作用。迄今在包括Nature、Science、Cell Metabolism在内的国际期刊发表学术论文20篇，引用逾6000次。</p>\n <h4 style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">荣誉奖励</h4>\n <p>2022 “清华-拜耳”研究员</p>\n <p>2021 基金委国家优秀青年基金（海外)</p>\n <p>2020美国国家卫生院青年科学家Pathway to Independence (NIH K99/R00) 职业发展奖</p>\n <p>2017美国血细胞癌与淋巴癌协会Leukemia &amp; Lymphoma Society 博士后研究基金</p>\n <p>2017美国生命科学基金会Life Sciences Research Foundation 博士后研究基金</p>\n <p>2017美国Susan G. Komen乳腺癌研究协会博士后研究基金</p>\n <p>2017美国国防部Horizon Award奖</p>\n <p>2015国家优秀自费留学生奖</p>\n <p>2010清华大学学业一等奖</p>\n <p>2008 清华大学生命科学学院郑格如奖学金</p>\n <h4 style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">代表性论文</h4>\n <p>1.Zhen Z, Ren J, Zhu J#. The redox requirement and regulation during cell proliferation. Trends Endocrinol Metab. 2024</p>\n <p>2.Zhu J# (co-correspondence), Wang H, Jiang X#. mTORC1 beyond anabolic metabolism: Regulation of cell death. J Cell Biol. 2022</p>\n <p>3.Pavlova NN*, Zhu J* (equal contribution), Thompson CB. The hallmarks of cancer metabolism: Still emerging. Cell Metabolism. 2022.</p>\n <p>4.Zhu J, Schwörer S, Berisa M, Kyung YJ, Ryu KW, Yi J, Jiang X, Cross JR, Thompson CB. Mitochondrial NADP(H) generation is essential for proline biosynthesis. Science. 2021.</p>\n <p>5.Yi J*, Zhu J* (equal contribution), Wu J, Thompson CB, Jiang X. Oncogenic activation of PI3K-AKT-mTOR signaling suppresses ferroptosis via SREBP-mediated lipogenesis. PNAS. 2020.</p>\n <p>6.Zhu J, Thompson CB. Metabolic control of cell growth and proliferation. Nature Reviews Mol Cell Biol 2019.</p>\n <p>7.Zhu J, Berisa M, Schwörer S, Qin W, Cross JR, Thompson CB. Transsulfuration activity can support cell growth upon extracellular cysteine limitation. Cell Metabolism. 2019.</p>\n <p>8.Zhu J, Dou Z, Sammons MA, Levine AJ, Berger SL. Lysine methylation represses p53 activity in teratocarcinoma cancer cells. PNAS. 2016.</p>\n <p>9.Sammons MA*, Zhu J* (equal contribution), Berger SL. A chromatin-focued siRNA screen for regulators of p53-dependent transcription. G3 (Genes Genomes Genetics). 2016.</p>\n <p>10.Zhu J, Sammons MA, Donahue G, Dou Z, Vedadi M, Getlik M, Barsyte-Lovejoy D, Al-awar R, Katona BW, Shilatifard A, Huang J, Hua X, Arrowsmith CH, Berger SL. Gain-of-function p53 mutants co-opt chromatin pathways to drive cancer growth. Nature. 2015.</p>\n <p>Complete list of publications:</p>\n <p class=\"vsbcontent_end\">https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=PYAk1M8AAAAJ&amp;hl=en</p>\n</div>\n<div></div>\n</div></div><div id=\"div_vote_id\"></div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n      \n\n</form>\n\n                      \n                    </div>\n                                      \n                </div>\n          <section class=\"n_sanji\">\n<ul style=\"    height: 44px;\">\n    <li><a href=\"../../szdw/jcyxy.htm\" title=\"教职员工\">教职员工</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"../../szdw/jzjs.htm\" title=\"兼职教授\">兼职教授</a></li>\n</ul>\n                  \n                </section>\n\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"mianbao\">\n            <div>\n     您现在的位置： \n                        <a href=\"../../index.htm\">首页</a>\n               <i>&gt;</i>\n                <a href=\"../../szdw/jcyxy.htm\">师资队伍</a>\n               <i>&gt;</i>\n                <a href=\"../../szdw/jcyxy.htm\">基础医学院</a>\n               <i>&gt;</i>\n                <a href=\"../../szdw/jcyxy/jyxl.htm\">教研系列</a>\n               <i>&gt;</i>\n                <a href=\"../../szdw/jcyxy/jyxl/zlswx.htm\">肿瘤生物学</a>\n               <i>&gt;</i>\n                正文\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"content_li1\"></div>\n        </div>\n    \n</section>\n<script>\n$('.miso_hd ul').miso({\n    autoplay:false,\n    slidesToShow: 3,\n    waitForAnimate: false,\n    asNavFor:$('.miso_bd')\n});\n$('.miso_bd').miso({\n    autoplay:false,\n    waitForAnimate: false,\n    adaptiveHeight:true,\n    asNavFor:$('.miso_hd ul')\n});\n</script>\n\n\n</section>\n\n<!--============================主体 结束=============================-->\n\n\n<!--============================底部 开始=============================-->\n\n\n<footer class=\"footer\">\n    <div class=\"w1200 clearfix\">\n        <div class=\"center fl\">\n    <a><img src=\"../../images/logo1.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-height: 55px;\"></a>\n\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"right fr\">\n   